"{\"uid\": \"dailypost.ng-2024-08-12-paris-olympics-its-quite-disheartening-chioma-ajunwa-bemoans-nigerias-outing\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Published  on  By  Nigeria's first Olympic gold medalist, Chioma Ajunwa, has described Nigeria's recent outing in Paris 2024 Olympics as disheartening.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19, \"end\": 26, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9833649100676085, \"rank\": 0.01691649639547459, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 58, \"end\": 71, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chioma_Ajunwa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chioma Ajunwa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chioma_Ajunwa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chioma_Ajunwa\"}, {\"begin\": 87, \"end\": 94, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9833649100676085, \"rank\": 0.01691649639547459, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She stated this on Monday while fielding questions on Arise Television's Morning Show programme.\", \"from\": 153, \"to\": 249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 207, \"end\": 212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ginnungagap\", \"score\": 0.9999998789987858, \"rank\": 1.1341108643035121e-07, \"text\": \"Arise\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ginnungagap\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ginnungagap\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"DAILY POST reported that Nigeria did not win any medal at the just concluded Olympics held in Paris, France.\", \"from\": 251, \"to\": 359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 251, \"end\": 261, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.209412104474665e-14, \"text\": \"DAILY POST\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_Daily_Post\"}, {\"begin\": 276, \"end\": 283, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9833649100676085, \"rank\": 0.01691649639547459, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}, {\"begin\": 345, \"end\": 350, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999974892934601, \"rank\": 2.5107127313709438e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 352, \"end\": 358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.4571008480404575, \"rank\": 0.7803793997263684, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reacting to the development, Ajunwa said it was unfortunate that the nation lost the whole chances, adding that athletes wasted their time, energy and resources.\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 522, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's quite disheartening that every year Nigeria tells this kind of story.\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you could remember, after the last Olympics before this, it was still the same thing.\", \"from\": 601, \"to\": 689, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You know they will keep on telling us.\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 730, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Oh, let them go back to the drawing board, the drawing board we never see; and we do not know how to draw on the board.\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's quite unfortunate that we have lost the whole chances.\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 912, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And the athletes to have wasted their time, their energy and their own personal resources.\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It is quite unfortunate that Nigeria spent so much, but that one is not my business because we do not spend that money when we are supposed to spend it,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1005, \"to\": 1169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1035, \"end\": 1042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"score\": 0.9833649100676085, \"rank\": 0.01691649639547459, \"text\": \"Nigeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EPL: De Ligt, Mazraoui in line to make Man Utd debut vs Fulham  NPFL: Akwa United boss Babaganaru reveals target ahead pre-season tourney  NNPP chieftain decries Nigeria's performance at Paris Olympic  'I am honoured' - Celine Dion relishes comeback performance at Paris Olympics opening ceremony  Paris Olympics: NOC sets target for athletes, administrators  Chioma Ajunwa: Lagos govt finally redeems house promise to Olympic gold medalist after 25 years  Copyright \\u00a9Daily Post Media Ltd\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1227, \"end\": 1233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fulham_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9999611301601617, \"rank\": 2.5376911180224207e-05, \"text\": \"Fulham\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fulham_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fulham_F.C.\"}, {\"begin\": 1235, \"end\": 1239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nigeria_Professional_Football_League\", \"score\": 0.9999999999947704, \"rank\": 5.304484517907353e-12, \"text\": \"NPFL\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.